---
const agents = [
  {
    icon: '💰', bg: 'from-[rgba(0,212,255,0.2)] to-[rgba(0,212,255,0.05)]',
    title: 'Agente de Ventas IA', tag: '24/7 Activo', col: 'text-primary',
    features: ['Califica leads con scoring automático', 'Envía propuestas con IA generativa', 'Seguimiento cada 24-48h automático', 'Detecta oportunidades de upsell'],
    metric: '340%', metricLabel: 'más conversiones',
  },
  {
    icon: '🛟', bg: 'from-[rgba(123,47,255,0.2)] to-[rgba(123,47,255,0.05)]',
    title: 'Agente de Soporte IA', tag: '80% Auto-resolución', col: 'text-[#B088FF]',
    features: ['Resuelve 80% de tickets sin humano', 'Consulta base de conocimiento en ≤1s', 'Genera y categoriza tickets solo', 'Escala con contexto completo'],
    metric: '2 min', metricLabel: 'resp. promedio',
  },
  {
    icon: '📣', bg: 'from-[rgba(255,45,120,0.2)] to-[rgba(255,45,120,0.05)]',
    title: 'Agente de Marketing IA', tag: 'Hiperpersonalización', col: 'text-accent',
    features: ['Segmenta audiencias por comportamiento', 'Elige el mejor horario de envío', 'Personaliza según historial de compras', 'Genera contenido por canal solo'],
    metric: '5x', metricLabel: 'tasa de apertura',
  },
  {
    icon: '📊', bg: 'from-[rgba(0,255,179,0.2)] to-[rgba(0,255,179,0.05)]',
    title: 'Agente de Datos IA', tag: 'Insights Proactivos', col: 'text-accent2',
    features: ['Reportes ejecutivos automáticos diarios', 'Detecta anomalías en tiempo real', 'Alertas proactivas al directivo', 'Predice tendencias con ML'],
    metric: '98%', metricLabel: 'precisión ML',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-[100px] relative" id="crm-agents">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-14">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[3px] text-primary uppercase bg-[rgba(0,212,255,0.08)] border border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.4)] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-5">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse-dot"></span>
        🤖 Agentes de Automatización IA
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-[clamp(32px,4vw,52px)] font-bold leading-[1.1] gradient-text mb-5">Tu equipo de robots<br/>que nunca descansa</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-[1.7] max-w-[580px] mx-auto">
        Cuatro agentes especializados que automatizan el 80% del trabajo repetitivo para que tu equipo se enfoque en lo que importa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-14">
      {agents.map(agent => (
        <div class="observe-anim bg-bg-card border border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.15)] rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.4)] hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex gap-3.5 items-center mb-5">
            <div class={`w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0 bg-gradient-to-br ${agent.bg}`}>{agent.icon}</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-1">{agent.title}</h3>
              <span class="font-mono text-[9px] bg-[rgba(0,212,255,0.1)] text-primary px-2 py-px rounded-full border border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.15)]">{agent.tag}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-auto text-right">
              <strong class={`font-display text-[22px] font-black ${agent.col}`}>{agent.metric}</strong>
              <p class="text-[9px] text-text-dim font-mono">{agent.metricLabel}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-1.5">
            {agent.features.map(f => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-text-muted">
                <span class={`text-[10px] font-bold ${agent.col}`}>→</span> {f}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- VoIP callout banner -->
    <div class="bg-bg-card border border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.2)] rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] gap-6 items-center">
      <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
        <div class="relative w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-glow-primary">
          📞
          <span class="absolute -top-0.5 -right-0.5 w-3 h-3 bg-accent2 rounded-full border-2 border-bg-dark animate-pulse-dot"></span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[3px] text-primary uppercase bg-[rgba(0,212,255,0.08)] border border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.4)] px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse-dot"></span>
            VoIP Integrado
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-[clamp(18px,2.5vw,26px)] font-bold text-white mb-2">Llamadas directas desde la App — sin costo adicional</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] text-text-muted leading-[1.6] max-w-[560px]">
            El cliente toca "Llamar", la IA evalúa y enruta en segundos. El agente ve todo el historial antes de contestar y recibe sugerencias en tiempo real.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 flex-shrink-0">
        {[
          { val: '2.1s',  label: 'Tiempo de conexión' },
          { val: '99.9%', label: 'Calidad de llamada' },
          { val: '0',     label: 'Costo por llamada' },
        ].map(s => (
          <div class="text-center bg-bg-card2 border border-[rgba(0,212,255,0.1)] rounded-xl px-5 py-2.5 min-w-[110px]">
            <strong class="font-display text-xl text-primary block">{s.val}</strong>
            <span class="font-mono text-[9px] text-text-dim">{s.label}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
